&lt;p&gt;PRACTICE NURSE NEEDED FOR A GENERAL PRACTICE IN LONDON BOROUGH OF BEXLEY&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a multi skilled team of Doctors, Nurse Practitioners, Nurses, Pharmacists, Physician Associates, HCAs and Medical Assistants supported by a superb administration team. We are looking to recruit an enthusiastic Practice Nurse to enhance our team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Practice has three GP Trainers. Nurses with relevant experience of medical specialities, ITU or casualty can be trained to be a practice nurse.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Practice is in the London Borough of Bexley. Central London is a 35 minute train journey or drive.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For inquiries contact Shelley Bhalla at shelley.bhalla@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
